00:02:50.200 --> 00:02:51.300
request to see

00:02:51.870 --> 00:02:52.800
the regional commanders

00:02:53.200 --> 00:02:53.950
of Long'an,

00:02:54.360 --> 00:02:56.530
Beiting, Fanyang, and Zhenxi.

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:17.020
