00:13:05.920 --> 00:13:07.220
The soldiers are examining the body.

00:13:08.550 --> 00:13:09.140
We found this

00:13:09.200 --> 00:13:10.440
on the horse.

00:16:36.320 --> 00:16:36.890
Let me.

00:16:45.750 --> 00:16:46.480
Give it to me.

