It matters to us too.

00:24:58.840 --> 00:24:59.570
Huai'an, don't worry.

00:25:01.310 --> 00:25:02.130
I will

00:25:02.990 --> 00:25:03.660
keep him safe.

00:25:04.440 --> 00:25:05.400
I will not let him

00:25:05.400 --> 00:25:06.360
fall into Yan Fengshan's hands.

00:25:08.030 --> 00:25:09.170
Go do what you must.

00:25:24.710 --> 00:25:25.420
Thank you.

00:25:27.630 --> 00:25:28.460
Now go.

00:25:35.160 --> 00:25:35.810
Use it for protection.

00:25:39.440 --> 00:25:39.810
Huai'an,

00:25:40.790 --> 00:25:42.180
your white hair draws too much attention.

00:25:43.120 --> 00:25:43.970
When you go out,

00:25:44.360 --> 00:25:45.290
wear a bamboo hat

00:25:45.710 --> 00:25:46.500
to cover it.

00:25:48.550 --> 00:25:49.180
Huai'an,

00:25:50.360 --> 00:25:51.290
you will come find us, right?

00:25:52.550 --> 00:25:53.750
Do not face

00:25:53.750 --> 00:25:54.520
Yan Fengshan alone.

00:25:55.680 --> 00:25:56.570
When it's time to kill him,

00:25:59.510 --> 00:26:00.330
bring the two of us with you.

00:26:00.880 --> 00:26:02.610
I have not finished this road yet.

00:26:03.960 --> 00:26:04.460
Of course

00:26:05.840 --> 00:26:06.700
I'll need you both.

00:26:18.960 --> 00:26:20.020
There was a scholar

00:26:20.880 --> 00:26:21.660
named Han Ziling.

00:26:22.790 --> 00:26:24.090
He asked me to give you

00:26:25.270 --> 00:26:26.020
this letter.

00:26:27.440 --> 00:26:28.460
He said he had

00:26:28.960 --> 00:26:29.700
long admired you.

00:26:30.750 --> 00:26:32.260
If anything happens to me,

00:26:34.440 --> 00:26:35.370
please give this

00:26:36.840 --> 00:26:37.290
to him.

00:26:41.880 --> 00:26:42.680
Remember:

00:26:44.120 --> 00:26:45.290
do not fail the expectations

00:26:46.750 --> 00:26:48.420
of the scholars of this realm.

00:26:51.230 --> 00:26:51.770
Live.

00:26:55.790 --> 00:26:56.260
I will.

00:27:02.310 --> 00:27:02.920
Now go.

00:28:05.200 --> 00:28:06.720
Why did you return to Chang'an?

00:28:10.310 --> 00:28:11.610
It was my fault.

00:28:21.400 --> 00:28:22.750
It was my fault.

00:28:26.100 --> 00:28:27.550
It was my fault.

00:28:41.360 --> 00:28:42.980
Humans belong to heaven and earth.

00:28:44.470 --> 00:28:45.940
Our souls come from the clouds,

00:28:47.070 --> 00:28:48.420
our bodies return to the earth.

00:28:51.600 --> 00:28:53.090
Heaven and earth leave traces on a person,

00:28:53.120 --> 00:28:54.090
and those traces

00:28:57.840 --> 00:28:58.850
can lead one back

00:29:01.030 --> 00:29:02.290
to where they once walked.

00:29:48.440 --> 00:29:49.020
Mother,

00:29:49.070 --> 00:29:50.260
I did something bad!

00:29:53.360 --> 00:29:54.020
Miss.

00:29:56.200 --> 00:29:56.900
Oh dear.

00:29:57.400 --> 00:29:58.180
I'm so sorry,

00:29:58.200 --> 00:29:59.080
truly sorry.

00:29:59.270 --> 00:29:59.940
Look at what you did.

00:30:00.060 --> 00:30:00.550
It's all right.

00:30:00.820 --> 00:30:01.680
He didn't do it on purpose.

00:30:01.970 --> 00:30:03.030
I simply happened to pass by.

00:30:03.930 --> 00:30:05.360
Miss, I'm really sorry.

00:30:06.060 --> 00:30:06.510
Why don't you

00:30:06.550 --> 00:30:08.260
come in and change into something clean?

00:30:09.100 --> 00:30:09.680
We have

00:30:09.860 --> 00:30:10.870
new clothes,

00:30:10.870 --> 00:30:11.400
all clean.

00:30:11.540 --> 00:30:12.230
They should

00:30:12.410 --> 00:30:13.360
fit you well.

00:30:13.620 --> 00:30:14.270
It's fine.

00:30:14.870 --> 00:30:15.680
I insist.

00:30:15.690 --> 00:30:16.790
It was my son's fault.

00:30:17.060 --> 00:30:18.200
With your clothes dirty,

00:30:18.210 --> 00:30:19.060
you must be uncomfortable.

00:30:19.340 --> 00:30:20.330
- Come on. - Thank you.

00:30:22.900 --> 00:30:24.680
We don't have much food to offer.

00:30:25.100 --> 00:30:26.070
Please make do.

00:30:26.540 --> 00:30:28.830
I've been living on cold, plain food along the way.

00:30:29.010 --> 00:30:30.070
A bowl of hot noodles

00:30:30.250 --> 00:30:31.030
is more than wonderful.

00:30:33.490 --> 00:30:34.470
What is he doing at the door?

00:30:36.060 --> 00:30:37.160
He's waiting for his father.

00:30:38.100 --> 00:30:40.070
His father works as a ferryman in Nanwei Trough,

00:30:41.010 --> 00:30:42.510
30 or 40 li from here.

00:30:43.060 --> 00:30:44.360
It's not easy for him to come back,

00:30:45.300 --> 00:30:46.960
but whenever he can find someone to take his place,

00:30:48.140 --> 00:30:49.680
even if it means walking a whole day and night,

00:30:50.410 --> 00:30:51.400
he'll come home to visit.

00:30:52.770 --> 00:30:53.990
Some spend their whole lives walking,

00:30:54.770 --> 00:30:56.120
just to make it home.

00:30:58.170 --> 00:30:59.070
You too, miss?

00:31:03.540 --> 00:31:04.720
I've lived in Chang'an for years.

00:31:05.100 --> 00:31:06.470
Now I miss home.

00:31:07.900 --> 00:31:10.030
Your father and mother

00:31:10.380 --> 00:31:11.600
must be longing for you too.

00:31:13.140 --> 00:31:14.200
To be missed by family

00:31:14.690 --> 00:31:15.640
is a blessing.

00:31:18.770 --> 00:31:20.360
I think I've heard that...

00:31:22.010 --> 00:31:23.260
My husband once said

00:31:23.300 --> 00:31:25.220
he had a ferryman companion.

00:31:25.820 --> 00:31:26.680
The man said he fled

00:31:26.690 --> 00:31:28.220
to Nanwei Trough with his little sister.

00:31:28.960 --> 00:31:29.900
Then

00:31:30.530 --> 00:31:31.310
his sister

00:31:31.340 --> 00:31:32.710
was taken in by a family,

00:31:33.210 --> 00:31:34.830
and he stayed behind,

00:31:35.660 --> 00:31:36.770
working as a ferryman

00:31:36.970 --> 00:31:38.050
while watching over her.

00:31:38.770 --> 00:31:40.880
He kept watch for seven whole years.

00:31:42.740 --> 00:31:43.540
I don't know what disaster

00:31:43.540 --> 00:31:44.510
struck their family.

00:31:45.170 --> 00:31:46.470
His sister was right beside him,

00:31:46.580 --> 00:31:47.360
yet they couldn't reunite.

00:31:48.170 --> 00:31:49.470
How bitter that must have been.

00:31:50.970 --> 00:31:52.280
That man also told my husband

00:31:52.450 --> 00:31:53.990
that having someone to worry about

00:31:54.170 --> 00:31:55.230
was a kind of blessing,

00:31:55.660 --> 00:31:56.440
just like you said.

00:32:03.470 --> 00:32:04.440
Is that ferryman

00:32:05.450 --> 00:32:06.700
still in Nanwei Trough?

00:32:08.490 --> 00:32:09.270
No.

00:32:09.590 --> 00:32:10.830
My husband said something happened,

00:32:11.060 --> 00:32:11.920
and he left.

00:32:13.410 --> 00:32:14.830
Let me light a lamp for my husband,

00:32:15.060 --> 00:32:15.950
so he knows

00:32:16.490 --> 00:32:18.790
my son and I are thinking of him.

00:32:50.970 --> 00:32:51.640
Sir.

00:32:53.060 --> 00:32:55.060
Miss, are you here to offer incense

00:32:55.260 --> 00:32:56.110
or seek a divination?

00:32:58.170 --> 00:32:59.030
I came to ask

00:32:59.030 --> 00:33:00.270
for a naming slip.

00:33:02.020 --> 00:33:03.590
Has a child been born at home?

00:33:04.340 --> 00:33:05.470
Congratulations.

00:33:06.300 --> 00:33:07.280
Is it a boy or a girl?

00:33:09.070 --> 00:33:10.110
Please, have a seat.

00:33:15.540 --> 00:33:16.570
It's not for a child.

00:33:17.170 --> 00:33:18.310
It's for myself.

00:33:20.040 --> 00:33:21.620
No one asks for a naming slip

00:33:21.810 --> 00:33:23.300
at your age.

00:33:26.690 --> 00:33:28.230
My family suffered a disaster when I was little.

00:33:29.340 --> 00:33:31.330
I was separated from a family member for many years.

00:33:33.300 --> 00:33:34.470
Recently, I found him again.

00:33:35.490 --> 00:33:36.400
This naming slip

00:33:36.660 --> 00:33:37.830
is to reclaim my true name

00:33:38.490 --> 00:33:39.510
and restore my ties with him.

00:33:44.410 --> 00:33:46.120
To spend half a lifetime adrift

00:33:46.820 --> 00:33:48.550
and still find your family again

00:33:50.300 --> 00:33:51.070
is no easy thing.

00:33:53.140 --> 00:33:54.230
Fate parts people

00:33:54.540 --> 00:33:56.880
but also brings them back together.

00:34:02.580 --> 00:34:05.180
So, for this naming slip, I will write...

00:34:07.300 --> 00:34:08.350
Do you still remember

00:34:08.540 --> 00:34:10.480
your name after all these years?

00:34:12.850 --> 00:34:13.520
My family name is Liu.

00:34:15.660 --> 00:34:16.560
I've carried this amulet

00:34:17.420 --> 00:34:18.830
for as long as I can remember.

00:34:20.100 --> 00:34:21.520
I never understood its meaning,

00:34:22.810 --> 00:34:23.600
but now I do.

00:34:27.660 --> 00:34:28.720
My given name is written on it.

00:34:29.400 --> 00:34:29.890
[Li]

00:34:29.890 --> 00:34:30.520
A single character:

00:34:31.460 --> 00:34:32.200
Li.

00:34:40.420 --> 00:34:42.120
Then for the blessing,

00:34:42.140 --> 00:34:44.160
I will write:

00:34:46.060 --> 00:34:47.270
"May you find home again

00:34:47.890 --> 00:34:49.480
and know lasting peace."

00:34:49.940 --> 00:34:50.720
How does that sound?

00:34:52.620 --> 00:34:53.480
Thank you, sir.

00:35:00.280 --> 00:35:05.000
[Liu Li: May you find home again and know lasting peace.]

00:35:05.000 --> 00:35:13.680
[Liu Li]

00:35:20.520 --> 00:35:22.600
[Bai Wan]

00:35:22.600 --> 00:35:25.120
[Liu Li]

00:35:31.730 --> 00:35:32.480
Liu Li,

00:35:34.540 --> 00:35:35.200
so you

00:35:38.840 --> 00:35:41.270
came back to reunite with me?

00:35:54.120 --> 00:35:57.240
[Liu Li]

00:36:35.770 --> 00:36:37.480
Take care. Goodbye.

00:36:38.520 --> 00:36:42.480
[Chen Zhiying of the Huben Army]

00:37:07.620 --> 00:37:08.750
Can you promise that?

00:37:10.500 --> 00:37:11.590
Of course I can.

00:37:11.740 --> 00:37:13.200
Then will you write to me

00:37:13.210 --> 00:37:14.270
to tell me you're safe?

00:37:15.330 --> 00:37:16.720
Wherever you go,

00:37:17.140 --> 00:37:18.350
write to me every year,

00:37:19.060 --> 00:37:20.000
so I know

00:37:20.330 --> 00:37:21.790
you're safe.

00:37:23.140 --> 00:37:24.600
She's your sister,

00:37:24.980 --> 00:37:26.350
yet you let her reunite with another family.

00:37:27.330 --> 00:37:28.560
You've been a ferryman here

00:37:29.060 --> 00:37:30.560
for seven years, three li from her home,

00:37:31.620 --> 00:37:33.000
just to protect her from afar.

00:37:33.980 --> 00:37:34.910
How long can you keep this up?

00:37:36.370 --> 00:37:37.120
I don't know.

00:37:39.290 --> 00:37:40.270
I only hope

00:37:42.060 --> 00:37:43.350
she never remembers her past.

00:37:58.170 --> 00:37:58.790
That night,

00:38:00.050 --> 00:38:01.270
I hid behind the wall

00:38:02.370 --> 00:38:04.040
and saw someone feeding you soup.

00:38:05.290 --> 00:38:06.290
You were

00:38:07.540 --> 00:38:08.950
surrounded by people

00:38:10.540 --> 00:38:11.270
who cared for you.

00:38:12.810 --> 00:38:13.950
At that moment,

00:38:14.390 --> 00:38:16.910
I decided to leave you with that family.

00:38:18.210 --> 00:38:19.040
I thought

00:38:20.580 --> 00:38:22.280
that if I was careful enough,

00:38:24.060 --> 00:38:25.720
you would live a safe life.

00:38:32.060 --> 00:38:32.680
Liu Li,

00:38:35.730 --> 00:38:37.270
I was wrong.

00:38:39.810 --> 00:38:40.790
When the time comes, I will reunite

00:38:42.420 --> 00:38:43.430
with you, Father, and Mother.

00:38:45.140 --> 00:38:46.230
The four of us

00:38:49.460 --> 00:38:50.200
will be together again.

00:39:05.800 --> 00:39:11.760
[Incense]

00:39:21.940 --> 00:39:22.480
Is it

00:39:22.940 --> 00:39:23.520
a funeral?

00:39:26.690 --> 00:39:27.790
The whole city is under martial law,

00:39:27.940 --> 00:39:29.040
killings everywhere.

00:39:29.370 --> 00:39:31.870
Even the city gates have changed hands several times.

00:39:32.580 --> 00:39:32.950
And you...

00:39:34.460 --> 00:39:36.480
You have to go through this on the very day

00:39:36.770 --> 00:39:37.950
the court is thrown into chaos.

00:39:39.770 --> 00:39:41.170
Everyone suffers.

00:39:41.500 --> 00:39:43.230
Everyone suffers!

00:39:44.500 --> 00:39:45.120
Sir,

00:39:45.330 --> 00:39:45.910
please come in.

00:39:50.060 --> 00:39:51.430
Do you need a memorial tablet made?

00:39:57.690 --> 00:39:58.560
Who

00:39:59.210 --> 00:39:59.910
is it for?

00:40:00.100 --> 00:40:00.750
What should it say?

00:40:05.370 --> 00:40:06.080
It is

00:40:08.170 --> 00:40:09.230
for my late sister, Liu Li.

00:40:18.640 --> 00:40:24.400
[Late Sister Liu Li]

00:41:06.170 --> 00:41:07.120
General Fengshan.

00:41:13.600 --> 00:41:17.560
[Yan Fengshan]

00:41:25.250 --> 00:41:26.350
In this courtyard,

00:41:27.660 --> 00:41:29.260
I can almost see the traces of my old friends.

00:41:30.580 --> 00:41:32.320
When you have time, ask around at the brokerages.

00:41:33.100 --> 00:41:34.120
If it can be bought,

00:41:34.730 --> 00:41:35.870
buy this place.

00:41:36.420 --> 00:41:37.790
It is indeed a fine courtyard.

00:41:38.850 --> 00:41:40.160
Convenient for cooking.

00:41:41.370 --> 00:41:43.000
I will go to the brokers tomorrow.

00:41:47.020 --> 00:41:47.520
General...

00:42:32.250 --> 00:42:34.270
The Liu family's child is buried here.

00:42:35.140 --> 00:42:36.120
From this day on,

00:42:36.940 --> 00:42:38.830
no one is allowed to set foot on this patch of land.

00:42:40.210 --> 00:42:40.680
Understood.

00:42:42.140 --> 00:42:42.640
General,

00:42:43.730 --> 00:42:44.870
we have taken the Imperial City.

00:42:45.460 --> 00:42:46.040
But

00:42:46.420 --> 00:42:47.350
the 400 men we first sent

00:42:47.370 --> 00:42:48.380
to assassinate Xiao Wuyang

00:42:48.810 --> 00:42:49.520
were all lost.

00:42:50.290 --> 00:42:51.950
We found no trace of him.

00:42:57.250 --> 00:42:57.870
What about Gu Yu?

00:42:58.210 --> 00:42:59.160
Gu Yu led

00:42:59.170 --> 00:43:00.040
two 100-man Baiwenhu units

00:43:00.250 --> 00:43:01.350
and tried to enter the Imperial City.

00:43:01.730 --> 00:43:02.560
We surrounded them.

00:43:03.140 --> 00:43:04.120
His men fought desperately

00:43:04.120 --> 00:43:05.120
to break him out.

00:43:05.940 --> 00:43:06.910
By the time they reached Yongchang Ward,

00:43:07.210 --> 00:43:08.310
all the Baiwenhu soldiers had fallen,

00:43:08.940 --> 00:43:09.480
and Gu Yu

00:43:10.330 --> 00:43:11.120
disappeared.

00:43:12.170 --> 00:43:14.230
Lock down the area surrounding the Imperial City,

00:43:14.770 --> 00:43:16.560
stretching west to Guangde Ward, east to Xuanyang Ward,

00:43:17.060 --> 00:43:18.680
and south to the outer streets

00:43:18.980 --> 00:43:19.680
of Jingzhao Prefecture.

00:43:20.730 --> 00:43:22.120
Both of them are injured.

00:43:22.500 --> 00:43:23.390
If they want to hide,

00:43:24.140 --> 00:43:25.560
it can only be within this area.

00:43:26.330 --> 00:43:27.350
Find them.

00:43:28.620 --> 00:43:29.040
Understood.

00:43:33.890 --> 00:43:34.870
All 12 gates of Chang'an

00:43:35.100 --> 00:43:36.600
are now under Huben guards' control.

00:43:37.500 --> 00:43:39.040
Xiao Wuyang stationed the Wuyang Army

00:43:39.170 --> 00:43:40.200
30 li outside the city,

00:43:41.250 --> 00:43:42.750
but as you ordered,

00:43:43.580 --> 00:43:44.830
the armies of the four regional commanders

00:43:44.850 --> 00:43:45.640
set out ahead of schedule

00:43:46.250 --> 00:43:48.200
and have now arrived near Chang'an.

00:43:48.980 --> 00:43:49.910
Their forces outnumber the Wuyang Army

00:43:49.940 --> 00:43:50.560
three to one

00:43:50.980 --> 00:43:52.120
and have kept them in check.

00:43:52.620 --> 00:43:53.750
Then that leaves

00:43:54.370 --> 00:43:55.680
only the north.

00:43:56.060 --> 00:43:57.270
Send a messenger to Tiemo

00:43:57.660 --> 00:43:58.640
and have them hold back

00:43:58.660 --> 00:43:59.480
the main Baiwenhu forces.

00:43:59.890 --> 00:44:01.080
As long as they don't march south,

00:44:02.250 --> 00:44:03.830
Chang'an is ours.

00:44:04.460 --> 00:44:05.160
I will go.

00:44:05.460 --> 00:44:06.160
Zhiying will handle it.

00:44:07.580 --> 00:44:08.230
Wang Pu,

00:44:08.810 --> 00:44:10.160
you carry a criminal record.

00:44:11.140 --> 00:44:14.480
Now, where is White Hair?

00:44:18.100 --> 00:44:18.790
He hasn't been found.

00:44:42.120 --> 00:44:44.960
[Late Sister Liu Li]

00:45:28.020 --> 00:45:28.910
White Hair!

00:46:02.140 --> 00:46:03.230
Do you yield?

00:46:05.620 --> 00:46:06.830
I will come back.

00:46:10.250 --> 00:46:11.860
And when I do, I will kill you.

00:47:13.520 --> 00:47:14.680
♪The wind never rests♪

00:47:15.240 --> 00:47:19.480
♪How much pain does it scatter to nothing?♪

00:47:20.800 --> 00:47:22.320
♪The rain knows no calm♪

00:47:22.520 --> 00:47:26.280
♪How much love does it cool into silence?♪

00:47:26.720 --> 00:47:28.720
♪All my life amid blades and shadows♪

00:47:28.720 --> 00:47:30.640
♪I live beside life and death♪

00:47:30.640 --> 00:47:33.760
♪In a landscape veiled in smoke and fire♪

00:47:33.760 --> 00:47:35.920
♪I can only live under a hidden name♪

00:47:35.920 --> 00:47:41.080
♪Even my sighs must fall softly♪

00:47:42.280 --> 00:47:43.560
♪The heart is unsteady♪

00:47:43.840 --> 00:47:48.360
♪How much hatred does it leave unnamed?♪

00:47:49.320 --> 00:47:51.080
♪The dream will not end♪

00:47:51.080 --> 00:47:55.200
♪How many lives does it bind to fate?♪

00:47:55.200 --> 00:47:57.200
♪Bearing my family's fate♪

00:47:57.480 --> 00:47:59.160
♪I can only stand firm♪

00:47:59.440 --> 00:48:02.120
♪I let my vows ring true♪

00:48:02.120 --> 00:48:05.080
♪So the common folk need not wander♪

00:48:05.080 --> 00:48:08.920
♪I have faith in it♪

00:48:09.240 --> 00:48:11.000
♪So I choose♪

00:48:11.000 --> 00:48:12.840
♪To cut off the past, to part in life♪

00:48:12.840 --> 00:48:13.600
♪Across thousands of li♪

00:48:13.600 --> 00:48:16.760
♪Who makes me vanish without a word?♪

00:48:16.760 --> 00:48:19.160
♪I seek refuge deep in the mountains♪

00:48:19.160 --> 00:48:23.080
♪Playing a game that spans ten long years♪

00:48:23.080 --> 00:48:25.840
♪At last I step out from every secret♪

00:48:25.840 --> 00:48:27.800
♪Standing opposed to both grace and grievance♪

00:48:28.040 --> 00:48:30.800
♪Without the slightest fear♪

00:48:30.800 --> 00:48:33.960
♪Along the ancient road, I spur my horse♪

00:48:34.360 --> 00:48:37.920
♪And ride away♪

00:48:37.920 --> 00:48:40.640
♪So I choose to cut off the past♪

00:48:40.640 --> 00:48:42.480
♪At sunset, beacon fires rise♪

00:48:42.480 --> 00:48:45.400
♪But I fear no bloodshed♪

00:48:45.400 --> 00:48:47.840
♪In the mortal world, I carry my pride♪

00:48:47.840 --> 00:48:51.760
♪News reaches me from Chang'an♪

00:48:51.760 --> 00:48:54.800
♪Along the way, I endure disgrace and set my schemes♪

00:48:54.800 --> 00:48:56.520
♪My blade falls upon my foes♪

00:48:56.520 --> 00:48:59.440
♪Then I leave the jianghu behind♪

00:48:59.440 --> 00:49:02.600
♪Traveling to the ends of the earth♪

00:49:02.600 --> 00:49:07.240
♪Disappearing into the wide world♪